  /**** DEFINITIONS FOR END-OF-SENTENCE DETECTION ****/

EOS_PUNCT [.!?]
ALL_EXCEPT_EOS_PUNCT  [^.!?]
EOS_ADD   [\'\"\)\]\}>]
