  /** but the scanners becomes very big (4 times) and about 3% slower with the lexicon abow **/
 /* HYPH_WORD ({HYPH_WORDS}|{HYPH_LEX}) */
  /** so we don't use it **/
HYPH_WORD {HYPH_WORDS}

